	"cabin_abandoned_closet": {
		"steps": [
			{
				"type": "text",
				"text": "You grab the closet handle and pull.\n\nCold air rushes out — and with it, something that should not be here. A pale shape coalesces from the dark, hollow and flickering.",
				"clear": true
			},
			{
				"type": "text",
				"text": "The spirit of the cabin's former owner fixes its empty gaze on you.",
				"clear": false,
				"no_wait": true
			},
			{
				"type": "combat",
				"enemy": "Restless Spirit",
				"on_victory": [
					{
						"type": "text",
						"text": "The spirit wavers and dissolves, scattering like smoke in the cold air.\n\nThe closet is empty. Just dusty clothes and an old hunting pack.",
						"clear": true
					},
					{
						"type": "set_var",
						"vars": {
							"cabin_closet_done": {
								"set": 1
							}
						}
					},
					{
						"type": "event",
						"event": "cabin_abandoned_choices"
					}
				]
			}
		]
	},
	"cabin_abandoned_drawer": {
		"steps": [
			{
				"type": "text",
				"text": "You pull the drawer open. Beneath a tangle of old wood and rusted nails, your hand finds a leather pouch.",
				"clear": true
			},
			{
				"type": "sfx",
				"sound": "chest_open"
			},
			{
				"type": "give_gold",
				"amount": 60
			},
			{
				"type": "text",
				"text": "You count out [color=yellow]60G[/color].",
				"clear": false
			},
			{
				"type": "set_var",
				"vars": {
					"cabin_drawer_done": {
						"set": 1
					}
				}
			},
			{
				"type": "event",
				"event": "cabin_abandoned_choices"
			}
		]
	},
	"cabin_abandoned_enter": {
		"steps": [
			{
				"type": "set_backdrop",
				"backdrop": "apple_werecabin.png"
			},
			{
				"type": "text",
				"text": "You push the door open. It groans on rusted hinges.\n\nThe inside is dim and disordered — a knocked-over chair, papers strewn across the floor, deep claw marks gouged into the walls and door frame. \nSomeone lived here, once. Not anymore.",
				"clear": false
			},
			{
				"type": "set_var",
				"vars": {
					"cabin_drawer_done": {
						"set": 0
					},
					"cabin_hearth_done": {
						"set": 0
					},
					"cabin_journals_done": {
						"set": 0
					},
					"cabin_closet_done": {
						"set": 0
					}
				}
			},
			{
				"type": "event",
				"event": "cabin_abandoned_choices"
			}
		]
	},
	"cabin_abandoned_hearth": {
		"steps": [
			{
				"type": "text",
				"text": "The ashes in the hearth are cold, but you find a dry log and coax a small fire to life.\n\nYou sit in its warmth for a while. It's the first moment of quiet you've had in the woods.",
				"clear": true
			},
			{
				"type": "sfx",
				"sound": "heal"
			},
			{
				"type": "effect",
				"effect": {
					"type": "heal",
					"amount": 25
				}
			},
			{
				"type": "text",
				"text": "You rest for a moment.\nHP restored by [color=green]25[/color].",
				"clear": false
			},
			{
				"type": "set_var",
				"vars": {
					"cabin_hearth_done": {
						"set": 1
					}
				}
			},
			{
				"type": "event",
				"event": "cabin_abandoned_choices"
			}
		]
	},
	"cabin_abandoned_journals": {
		"steps": [
			{
				"type": "text",
				"text": "Three journals, water-warped and bound together with a leather strap. You open the most recent one.",
				"clear": true
			},
			{
				"type": "text",
				"text": "\"Day 12\n — The beast's tracks are unmistakable. I've seen wolf prints before. These are different — the gait too long, too deliberate. Whatever walks Apple Woods wears the shape of a wolf but not the nature of one.\nI'll find it.\"",
				"clear": false
			},
			{
				"type": "text",
				"text": "\"Day 19\n — It knows I'm here. I came back to camp and found everything moved. Nothing taken — just rearranged. Like it was making a point. I haven't slept properly in days. The apples taste strange after dark.\"",
				"clear": false
			},
			{
				"type": "text",
				"text": "\"Day 24\n — The scratches appeared on the door last night. Deep ones. I didn't hear a sound.\n\nIf someone finds this — the creature was once a man. A hunter, like me. I saw it in his eyes.\n\nDon't let it —\n \"\n\n[The entry ends here. The rest of the page is torn away.]",
				"clear": false
			},
			{
				"type": "set_var",
				"vars": {
					"cabin_journals_done": {
						"set": 1
					}
				}
			},
			{
				"type": "event",
				"event": "cabin_abandoned_choices"
			}
		]
	},
